<!--
================================================================================
InvoicePDF_Focusnext — Visualforce PDF (Header Documentation)
================================================================================
Purpose
- Render a branded, two-page PDF invoice for Invoice__c records (Focusnext).
- First page: large title, project name, date, invoice number, optional Swiss QR-bill image.
- Subsequent pages: running header/logo, running footer, recipient address block, invoice meta,
  grouped/non-grouped line items, totals, payment terms, and bank details.

Entry / Invocation
- Page: <apex:page ... renderAs="pdf" ...>
- Standard controller: Invoice__c
- Extension: InvoiceDocumentController
- Example: /apex/InvoicePDF_Focusnext?id=<Invoice__c.Id>

Internationalization (PDF language)
- language="{!IF(invoiceRecord.AccountLanguage__c == 'DE', 'de_CH', 'en_CH')}"
- Dates/period strings come from controller properties:
  - {!localisedDate}, {!localisedPeriodFrom}, {!localisedPeriodUntil}
- Custom Labels used:, 
    Focusnext_Footer1, BLC_Footer2, Focusnext_Footer3, InvoiceNr, Offertnummer, your_reference, po_nr, Period, 
    Total_Amount, VAT_Amount, Total_Gross, INKL_VAT, TermsPayment, VAT_Footer, IBAN, Bank_Clearing, SWIFT

Branding & Static Resources
- Header logo: $Resource.focusnext_logo (width=200).
- Running header/footers are generated with CSS @page + element().

Controller Contract (InvoiceDocumentController)
- Exposes:
  - invoiceRecord (Invoice__c), including related fields (see “Fields read”).
  - localisedDate, localisedPeriodFrom, localisedPeriodUntil (Strings).
  - termsOfPaymentLabel (String).
  - imageURL (String URL for Swiss QR-bill image).
  - mapInvPosGroup (Map<String, List<InvoicePosition__c>>): grouped positions.
  - mapGroupNameAmount (Map<String, InvoicePosition__c or DTO>): group headers with sums.
  - nonGroupInvPos (List<InvoicePosition__c>): positions without a group.
  - Action method getImageURL (invoked by page ‘action’ attribute) must populate imageURL.
- Required behavior:
  - imageURL must be resolvable before first render (for the first-page image).
  - localised* values must match page language and account locale rules.

Data Model — Fields Read
- Invoice__c:
  - InvoiceTitle__c
  - ProjectName__r.Name
  - AccountLanguage__c
  - InvoiceStatus__c (used to show "DRAFT Invoice" vs InvoiceDocumentNr__c)
  - InvoiceDocumentNr__c
  - InvoiceReceiver__r.BillingCountry__c (controls Swiss QR-bill image)
  - AccountNameLegal__c
  - BillingNameAddition__c
  - BillingAddressStreetNr__c
  - BillingAddressAddition__c
  - BillingAddressPOBox__c
  - BillingAddressZIP__c
  - BillingAdressCity__c  <-- NOTE: field API name contains "Adress" (single 'd')
  - BillingAddressState__c
  - BillingAddressCountry__c
  - OpportunityQuoteNr__c
  - InvoiceContact__r.FirstName / LastName / Phone / Email
  - CustomerReference__c, CustomerOrderNr__c
  - ShowProjectInvoiceDescription__c, InvoiceDescription__c
  - ProjectInvoiceCurrency__c
  - VATPercent__c
  - InvoiceTotalAmountNet__c, InvoiceVATAmount__c, InvoiceTotalAmountGross__c
  - BankName__c, BankLocation__c, IBAN__c, BankClearing__c, SWIFT__c
- InvoicePosition__c (or DTO in repeats):
  - InvoicePositionName__c
  - InvoicePositionAmount__c
  - InvoicePositionText__c

Page Structure & Rendering Notes
- PDF engine: Visualforce PDF (Flying Saucer). Uses CSS3 Paged Media features:
  - @page :first — unique margins and a bottom-left image area (imageFirstPage).
  - @page — running header/footer on subsequent pages via position: running(name).
  - element(header) and element(footer) supply repeating content.
- Head / Body tags disabled:
  - standardStylesheets="false" applyHtmlTag="false" applyBodyTag="false"
- First page (”.contentFirstPage”):
  - Large title (InvoiceTitle__c), Project name, date, InvoiceNr/DRAFT status.
  - Shows Swiss QR-bill image only if BillingCountry__c == 'SWITZERLAND':
    <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!invoiceRecord.InvoiceReceiver__r.BillingCountry__c == 'SWITZERLAND'}">
      <apex:image url="{!imageURL}" .../>
- Second page and onward:
  - Recipient address block composed from invoiceRecord address fields
    (panels hide empty lines via rendered and “hidden” CSS class).
  - Right column shows InvoiceNr/Offertnummer and Invoice Contact details plus reference/PO meta.
  - Section with date/title/project and optional invoice description.
  - Line items:
    - Grouped: mapInvPosGroup (group name) with mapGroupNameAmount for per-group sum.
    - Non-grouped: nonGroupInvPos.
    - If InvoicePositionText__c present, position row is bold + has a following description row.
  - Totals block: Net, VAT (with percent), Gross (uppercase + currency + “inkl. VAT” label).
  - Terms and VAT notes, then bank details.
- Pagination helpers:
  - .page-break class (not currently used in loops).
  - -fs-table-paginate: paginate for tables.

Styling / Layout
- Fonts: Helvetica (fallback sans-serif).
- Font utilities: .font70/80/90/100/110/120/130, .bold, .uppercase, .alignRight, .colorGray.
- Spacing utilities: paddingTop/Bottom variants, paddingGroup, margin helpers.
- Table columns: tableLargeCol (90%), tableSmallCol (10%) for amount column alignment.
- Borders: .borderBottom, .borderBottomLarge; highlight line beneath headings.
- Margins:
  - @page :first — bottom margin large to accommodate imageFirstPage at bottom.
  - Subsequent @page — top-center running header, bottom-center running footer.

Feature Flags / Conditional Rendering
- Draft watermark logic via:
  - IF(InvoiceStatus__c = 'Draft', 'DRAFT Invoice', InvoiceDocumentNr__c)
- Swiss QR-bill image only for Switzerland billing country.
- Optional fields (address lines, phone, quote number, references, description) hidden when blank.

Gotchas / Known Quirks
- Field API “BillingAdressCity__c” (single ‘d’) is intentional; do not rename without code changes.
- Paged-media CSS support varies; rely on Flying Saucer features used here (element(), @page).
- Avoid injecting <body>/<html> tags due to apply*Tag="false".
- Ensure imageURL is absolute or resolvable in PDF context (controller action sets it).

Dependencies
- Apex: InvoiceDocumentController (provides data, i18n strings, and imageURL).
- Static Resource: focusnext_logo.
- Custom Labels listed above.

Change Log
- david@inspireAi -- 2025-10-23

https://brandleadership--dev1--c.sandbox.vf.force.com/apex/InvoicePDF_Focusnext?id=a0QFT000007lLI02AM
================================================================================
-->
<apex:page standardController="Invoice__c" extensions="InvoiceDocumentController" showHeader="false" sidebar="false"
    renderAs="pdf" standardStylesheets="false" applyHtmlTag="false" applyBodyTag="false" action="{!getImageURL}" language="{!IF(invoiceRecord.AccountLanguage__c == 'DE', 'de_CH', 'en_CH')}">
    
    <head>
        <style>
          
            @page :first {
                margin-bottom: 360px !important;
                margin-left: 0 !important;
                margin-right: 0 !important;
                font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;

                @bottom-left {
                    content: element(imageFirstPage);
                }
                @bottom-center{

                }
                @top-center {
                    /*nothing*/
                }
            }

            @page {
                margin-top: 150px !important;
                margin: .50in .70in 1in 0.80in;
                font-size: 70%;
                font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
                
                @top-center {
                    content: element(header);
                }
                @bottom-center {
                    font-size: 65%;
                    content: element(footer);
                    font-weight: normal;
                }
            }

            .page-break {
                display: block;
                page-break-after: always;
            }

            div.header {
              display: block;
              position: running(header);
              font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
            }
            div.footer {
                display: block;
                font-size: 55%;
                text-align: center;
                position: running(footer);
                font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
            }

            div.content table {
                -fs-table-paginate: paginate;
            }

            .p {
                page-break-inside: avoid;
                font-weight: normal;
            }
            
            .head_col_1 {
                width: 35%;
            }
            .head_col_2 {
                width: 30%;
            }
            .head_col_3 {
                width: 35%;
            }

            .col_1 {
                width: 25%;
                vertical-align: top;
            }
            .col_2 {
                width: 20%;
            }
            .col_3 {
                width: 25%;
                
            }
            .contentFirstPage {
              font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
            }

            .col35{
                width: 33%;
            }
            .col50{
                width: 50%;
            }
            .tableLargeCol{
                width: 90%;
            }
            .tableSmallCol{
                width: 10%;
                align-content: right;
            }
            .borderBottom{
                border-bottom: 0.5pt solid black;
            }
            .borderBottomLarge {
                border-bottom: 1pt solid black;
            }
            .highlight{
                /*font-weight: bold;*/
                border-bottom: 3pt solid black;
            }

            .content{
                padding-top: 10px;
                font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
            }
            
            .textFirstPage{
                padding-top: 160px;
                margin: .50in .70in 1in 1.25in;
                width: 100%;
            }
            .projNameFirstPage{
                padding-top:15px;
                padding-bottom: 25px;
                width: 200px;
            }
            div.imageFirstPage{
                display: block;
                object-fit: cover;
                position: running(imageFirstPage);
            }

            /* Font size */
            .font70 {
              font-size: 70%;
            }
            .font80 {
              font-size: 80%;
            }
            .font90 {
              font-size: 90%;
            }
            .font100 {
              font-size: 100%;
            }
            .font110 {
              font-size: 110%;
            }
            .font120 {
              font-size: 120%;
            }
            .font130 {
              font-size: 130%;
            }
            .bold{
              font-weight: bold;
            }
            .uppercase {
              text-transform: uppercase;
            }
            .alignRight{
              text-align: right;
            }
            .colorGray {
              color: rgb(69, 69, 69);
            }

            /* Paddings */
            .paddingFirstTable{
                padding-top: -50px;
            }
            .paddingTopTable{
                padding-top: 15px;
            }
            .paddingBottom10{
                padding-bottom: 10px;
            }
            .paddingBottom20{
                padding-bottom: 20px;
            }
            .paddingBotom30{
                padding-bottom: 20px;
            }
            .paddingTop10{
                padding-top: 10px;
            }
            .paddingTop20{
                padding-top: 20px;
            }
            .paddingTop30{
                padding-top:30px;
            }
            .paddingTop40{
                padding-top: 40px;
            }
            .rightColPadding{
                padding-top: 20px;
            }
            .paddingGroup{
                padding-top: 25px;
            }
            .margin_bottom{
                padding-bottom: 30px;
            }
            .hidden {
                display: none;
            }
        </style>
    </head>

    <div class="header">
        <table>
                <tr>
                    <th class="head_col_1">
                    </th>
                    <th class="head_col_2">
                        <apex:image url="{!$Resource.focusnext_logo}" width="200" />
                    </th>
                    <th class="head_col_3">
                    </th>
                </tr>
            </table>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer colorGray">
        <span class="bold">{!$Label.Focusnext_Footer1} </span><br/>
        {!$Label.BLC_Footer2} <br/>
        {!$Label.Focusnext_Footer3}<br/>
    </div>

    <!-- FIRST PAGE -->
    <div class="contentFirstPage" >
        <div class="textFirstPage">
          <table>
              <tr>
                <td class="bold font110 uppercase">
                    <apex:outputText value="{!invoiceRecord.InvoiceTitle__c}"></apex:outputText>
                </td>    
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class=" bold font130 paddingBottom20" style="padding-right:2in;">
                    <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.ProjectName__r.Name}"></apex:outputField>
                </td>    
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="paddingBottom20">
                    {!localisedDate}
                </td>    
              </tr>
          
              <tr>
                  <td class="font80">
                      {!$Label.InvoiceNr}:
                  </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                  <td class="font80">
                      <apex:outputText value="{!IF(invoiceRecord.InvoiceStatus__c = 'Draft', 'DRAFT Invoice',invoiceRecord.InvoiceDocumentNr__c)}" />
                  </td>
              </tr>
          </table>
        </div>


        <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!invoiceRecord.InvoiceReceiver__r.BillingCountry__c == 'SWITZERLAND' &&
                                    (invoiceRecord.ProjectInvoiceCurrency__c == 'CHF' || invoiceRecord.ProjectInvoiceCurrency__c == 'EUR')}">
            <div class="imageFirstPage" style="margin:0; padding:0;">
                <apex:image url="{!imageURL}" width="815px" style="max-width:815px;" />
            </div>
        </apex:outputPanel>
    </div>
    
    <!-- SECOND PAGE -->
    <div style="page-break-before:always;" class="content">
        <body style="font-size:85%;font-weight:normal; font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;color:#010101">
            <!-- Titles -->
            <div style="width: 75%;">
                <div style="height: 150px;">
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="block" styleClass="{!IF(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.AccountNameLegal__c), 'hidden', '')}" rendered="{!NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.AccountNameLegal__c))}">
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.AccountNameLegal__c}" /><br/>
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="block" styleClass="{!IF(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingNameAddition__c), 'hidden', '')}" rendered="{!NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingNameAddition__c))}">
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.BillingNameAddition__c}" /><br/>
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="block" styleClass="{!IF(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAddressStreetNr__c), 'hidden', '')}" rendered="{!NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAddressStreetNr__c))}">
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.BillingAddressStreetNr__c}" /><br/>
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="block" styleClass="{!IF(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAddressAddition__c), 'hidden', '')}" rendered="{!NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAddressAddition__c))}">
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.BillingAddressAddition__c}" /><br/>
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="block" styleClass="{!IF(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAddressPOBox__c), 'hidden', '')}" rendered="{!NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAddressPOBox__c))}">
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.BillingAddressPOBox__c}" /><br/>
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="inline" styleClass="{!IF(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAddressZIP__c), 'hidden', '')}" rendered="{!NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAddressZIP__c))}">
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.BillingAddressZIP__c}" />&nbsp;
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="inline" styleClass="{!IF(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAdressCity__c), 'hidden', '')}" rendered="{!NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAdressCity__c))}">
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.BillingAdressCity__c}" /><br/>
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="block" styleClass="{!IF(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAddressState__c), 'hidden', '')}" rendered="{!NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAddressState__c))}">
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.BillingAddressState__c}" /><br/>
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="block" styleClass="{!IF(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAddressCountry__c), 'hidden', '')}" rendered="{!NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.BillingAddressCountry__c))}">
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.BillingAddressCountry__c}" /><br/>
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                </div>
                <div class="alignRight" style="margin-top:-120px;">
                    <div class="bold" >{!$Label.InvoiceNr}:</div>
                    <apex:outputText value="{!IF(invoiceRecord.InvoiceStatus__c = 'Draft', 'DRAFT Invoice',invoiceRecord.InvoiceDocumentNr__c)}" />
                    <apex:outputText styleClass="bold" rendered="{!!ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.OpportunityQuoteNr__c)}" value="{!$Label.Offertnummer}:"></apex:outputText><br/>
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="block" styleClass="{!IF(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.OpportunityQuoteNr__c), 'hidden', '')}">
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.OpportunityQuoteNr__c}" /><br/>
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                    <div class=" paddingTop10 bold">
                        {!$Label.InvoiceContact}:
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.InvoiceContact__r.FirstName}"></apex:outputField>&nbsp;
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.InvoiceContact__r.LastName}"></apex:outputField><br/>
                        <apex:outputPanel layout="block" styleClass="{!IF(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.InvoiceContact__r.Phone), 'hidden', '')}">
                            <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.InvoiceContact__r.Phone}" /><br/>
                        </apex:outputPanel>
                        <apex:outputText value="{!invoiceRecord.InvoiceContact__r.Email}"></apex:outputText><br/>
                    </div>

                    <apex:outputPanel layout="none">
                        <br/>
                        <!-- Bold label line -->
                        <span class="rightColPadding bold">
                            <apex:outputText value="{!$Label.your_reference}"
                                rendered="{!NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.CustomerReference__c))}" />

                            <apex:outputText value="&nbsp;/&nbsp;" escape="false"
                                rendered="{!AND(NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.CustomerReference__c)),
                                                NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.CustomerOrderNr__c)))}" />

                            <apex:outputText value="{!$Label.po_nr}"
                                rendered="{!NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.CustomerOrderNr__c))}" />

                            <apex:outputText value=":" 
                                rendered="{!OR(NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.CustomerReference__c)),
                                            NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.CustomerOrderNr__c)))}" />
                        </span>
                        <br/>
                        <!-- Non-bold values -->
                        <span class="rightColPadding">
                            <apex:outputText value="{!invoiceRecord.CustomerReference__c}"
                                rendered="{!NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.CustomerReference__c))}" />

                            <apex:outputText value="&nbsp;/&nbsp;" escape="false"
                                rendered="{!AND(NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.CustomerReference__c)),
                                                NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.CustomerOrderNr__c)))}" />

                            <apex:outputText value="{!invoiceRecord.CustomerOrderNr__c}"
                                rendered="{!NOT(ISBLANK(invoiceRecord.CustomerOrderNr__c))}" />
                        </span>
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                </div>
            </div>          

            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td class="paddingBottom20 ">
                        {!localisedDate}
                    </td>    
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="bold font90 uppercase">
                        <apex:outputText value="{!invoiceRecord.InvoiceTitle__c}"></apex:outputText>
                    </td>    
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="font110 bold uppercase paddingBottom20 paddingTop10" style="padding-right:2in;">
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.ProjectName__r.Name}"></apex:outputField>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="bold">
                        {!$Label.Period}:
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="paddingBottom10">
                        {!localisedPeriodFrom} - {!localisedPeriodUntil}
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <apex:outputField rendered="{!invoiceRecord.ShowProjectInvoiceDescription__c == true}" value="{!invoiceRecord.InvoiceDescription__c}"></apex:outputField> 
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <!-- MAIN TABLE -->

            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="75%">
                <tr >
                    <td class="tableLargeCol"> </td>
                    <td class="tableSmallCol alignRight bold"> {!invoiceRecord.ProjectInvoiceCurrency__c}</td>
                </tr>

                <!-- <apex:repeat value="{!mapInvPosGroup}" var="groupName" > -->
                <apex:repeat value="{!invPosGroupKeys}" var="groupName" >
                    <!-- Invoice positions group -->
                    <tr>
                        <td class="tableLargeCol bold paddingGroup borderBottom highlightLight" ><apex:outputField value="{!mapGroupNameAmount[groupName].InvoicePositionName__c}"/> </td>
                        <td class="tableSmallCol alignRight bold  paddingGroup borderBottom highlightLight"> <apex:outputField value="{!mapGroupNameAmount[groupName].InvoicePositionAmount__c}"/></td>
                    </tr>
                    
                    <!-- Invoice positions belonging to the group -->
                    <apex:repeat value="{!mapInvPosGroup[groupName]}" var="invPos" >
                        <tr>
                            <apex:outputPanel layout="none" rendered="{!!(ISBLANK(invPos.InvoicePositionText__c))}">
                                <td class="tableLargeCol paddingTopTable bold ">
                                    <apex:outputField value="{!invPos.InvoicePositionName__c}"/>
                                </td>
                                <td class="tableSmallCol alignRight paddingTopTable">
                                <!-- JC updated 25/03/2026 from the following line to the rest of the code inside this td
                                    <apex:outputField value="{!invPos.InvoicePositionAmount__c}"/>
                                -->
                                    <apex:outputPanel layout="none" rendered="{!invPos.ShowPositionAmount__c}">
                                    <apex:outputField value="{!invPos.InvoicePositionAmount__c}"/>
                                    </apex:outputPanel>
                                </td>
                            </apex:outputPanel>
                            <apex:outputPanel layout="none" rendered="{!(ISBLANK(invPos.InvoicePositionText__c))}">
                                <td class="tableLargeCol paddingTopTable bold borderBottom highlightLight">
                                    <apex:outputField value="{!invPos.InvoicePositionName__c}"/>
                                </td>
                                <td class="tableSmallCol alignRight paddingTopTable borderBottom highlightLight">
                                    <apex:outputField value="{!invPos.InvoicePositionAmount__c}"/>
                                </td>
                            </apex:outputPanel>
                        </tr>
                        <apex:outputPanel layout="none" rendered="{!!(ISBLANK(invPos.InvoicePositionText__c))}">
                            <tr>
                                <td class="tableLargeCol borderBottom highlightLight">
                                    <apex:outputField value="{!invPos.InvoicePositionText__c}"/>
                                </td>
                                <td class="tableSmallCol alignRight paddingTopTable borderBottom highlightLight">
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </apex:outputPanel>
                    </apex:repeat>
                </apex:repeat>

                <apex:repeat value="{!nonGroupInvPos}" var="invPos">
                    <tr>
                        <apex:outputPanel layout="none" rendered="{!!(ISBLANK(invPos.InvoicePositionText__c))}">
                            <td class="tableLargeCol paddingTopTable bold">
                                <apex:outputField value="{!invPos.InvoicePositionName__c}"/>
                            </td>
                            <td class="tableSmallCol alignRight paddingTopTable bold">
                                <apex:outputField value="{!invPos.InvoicePositionAmount__c}"/>
                            </td>
                        </apex:outputPanel>
                        <apex:outputPanel layout="none" rendered="{!(ISBLANK(invPos.InvoicePositionText__c))}">
                            <td class="tableLargeCol paddingTopTable bold borderBottom highlightLight">
                                <apex:outputField value="{!invPos.InvoicePositionName__c}"/>
                            </td>
                            <td class="tableSmallCol alignRight paddingTopTable borderBottom highlightLight">
                                <!-- JC updated 25/03/2026 from the following line to the rest of the code inside this td
                                    <apex:outputField value="{!invPos.InvoicePositionAmount__c}"/>
                                -->
                                    <apex:outputPanel layout="none" rendered="{!invPos.ShowPositionAmount__c}">
                                    <apex:outputField value="{!invPos.InvoicePositionAmount__c}"/>
                                    </apex:outputPanel>
                            </td>
                        </apex:outputPanel>
                    </tr>
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="none" rendered="{!!(ISBLANK(invPos.InvoicePositionText__c))}">
                        <tr>
                            <td class="tableLargeCol borderBottom highlightLight">
                                <apex:outputField value="{!invPos.InvoicePositionText__c}"/>
                            </td>
                            <td class="tableSmallCol alignRight paddingTopTable borderBottom highlightLight">
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                </apex:repeat>

                <!--AFTER LOOP Total Amounts-->

                <tr >
                    <td class="tableLargeCol  borderBottomLarge paddingTop40 bold">{!$Label.Total_Amount} </td>
                    <td class="tableSmallCol borderBottomLarge alignRight paddingTop40 bold" > 
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.InvoiceTotalAmountNet__c}"></apex:outputField>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <td class="tableLargeCol borderBottom paddingTopTable">{!$Label.VAT_Amount} &nbsp;{!invoiceRecord.VATPercent__c} </td>
                    <td class="tableSmallCol borderBottom alignRight paddingTopTable"> 
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.InvoiceVATAmount__c}"></apex:outputField>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <td class="tableLargeCol  borderBottomLarge uppercase paddingTopTable bold">{!$Label.Total_Gross} {!invoiceRecord.ProjectInvoiceCurrency__c} {!$Label.INKL_VAT} </td>
                    <td class="tableSmallCol borderBottomLarge alignRight paddingTopTable bold"> 
                        <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.InvoiceTotalAmountGross__c}"></apex:outputField>
                    </td>
                </tr>

            </table>

            <div class="paddingBotom10 paddingTop30 ">
                 {!$Label.TermsPayment}&nbsp;{!termsOfPaymentLabel}
            </div>
            <div class="paddingBotom30 ">
                 {!$Label.VAT_Footer}
            </div>
            <div class="">
                <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.BankName__c}"></apex:outputField>,&nbsp;
                <apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.BankLocation__c}"></apex:outputField><br/>
                {!$Label.IBAN}&nbsp;<apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.IBAN__c}"></apex:outputField>,
                {!$Label.Bank_Clearing}&nbsp;<apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.BankClearing__c}"></apex:outputField>,
                {!$Label.SWIFT}&nbsp;<apex:outputField value="{!invoiceRecord.SWIFT__c}"></apex:outputField>
            </div>
        </body>
    </div>

</apex:page>